{
  "texts": [
    "While this technology can be used to generate fake [52], unsafe content [75] or facilitate censorship [74], LLMs also offer new possibilities for content analysis, including detection of false and misleading information.",
    "This particular task has been attracting a growing amount of scholarly interest (e.g.",
    "[38]), but its realisation remains rather challenging due to difficulties of automated evaluation of information veracity (e.g.",
    "[3]).Despite the initially promising findings concerning the potential of LLMs to facilitate political communication research [38,72], there are still important gaps which require addressing.",
    "Similar to search engines and platforms mediated by nongenerative forms of AI, generative AI technology is largely non-transparent for its users [43]."
  ]
}